Maaaring mahirap ito

00:35:19.840 --> 00:35:21.500
gamit lamang ang aking maliit na kayamanan.

00:35:22.440 --> 00:35:23.500
Pero hindi ako pwedeng sumuko.

00:35:23.840 --> 00:35:24.560
Kaya,

00:35:24.920 --> 00:35:25.960
Susubukan ko ang aking makakaya

00:35:26.360 --> 00:35:27.820
na manatiling isang babaeng tycoon.

00:35:29.400 --> 00:35:31.880
